{"tid":2440990,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國指中國種族滅絕新疆維族人　中方批評美方撒謊","createTime":"2021-03-10T10:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T11:51:19.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b1f3415f327d481a81932481be0e3afab3fd98c0","tid":2440990,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"美國指中國種族滅絕新疆維族人 中方批評美方撒謊<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579805-20210310.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579805-20210310.htm&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwpldMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=a84ee45f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579805-20210310.htm&h=1770df3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579805-20210310.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1579805_1_L_20210310165226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1579805_1_L_20210310165226.jpg&h=17d24d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙立堅稱，中方堅決反對在人權問題上撒謊、造謠，打著人權旗號干涉別國內政。（路透社資料圖片）<br />\n美國國務院發言人普萊斯早前表示，中國對新疆維吾爾族人犯下種族滅絕與反人類罪行。在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅批評說法荒謬絕倫，與事實完全相反，是別有用心的造謠和徹頭徹尾的謊言，要求美方拿出證據。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅重申，新疆維吾爾族人口從555萬增長到1200多萬，質疑種族滅絕的說法。他又諷刺美國殺害印第安人的歷史，暗示「有人更適合戴上種族滅絕的帽子」，認為美方應該首先關注和改善自身存在的人權問題，中方堅決反對在人權問題上撒謊、造謠，打著人權旗號干涉別國內政。"},{"pid":"9a49d3e346e24b81542f35274eb8eda21682d6d6","tid":2440990,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T11:00:04.000Z","msg":"咁打未？"},{"pid":"b2b3ac8aa49ba603bbd75c6c7bd9e8161117151b","tid":2440990,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"石頭 腳"}]}